name: "Pansexual Macarons" by Sunny Crittenden
description: In honour of Pride Month 2021 & #PicEtNunc100 I'm minting my photo of macarons the colours of the pansexual flag. These colours are my signature palette when making art, chosen long before I even knew the term "pansexual" & as it turns out, I AM pansexual! Happy Pride!🌈
